{"title":"Windows安装Python环境","date":"2023-07-28T17:40:19.029Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2023年7月28日","L":"2023/07/28","MM-DD":"07-28"},"link":"2023/07/28/Windows安装Python环境","updated":"2023-07-28T08:54:19.870Z","content":"<p><strong>Windows安装Python环境</strong><br>\n<strong>1、首先下载Python的环境软件</strong><br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210308205235264.png\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n2、以<strong>管理员身份</strong>运行python-3.7.4-amd64-环境.exe<br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210308205923290.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3UwMTQyOTI0MDI=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210308210034676.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3UwMTQyOTI0MDI=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/2021030821023789.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3UwMTQyOTI0MDI=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n<strong>3、安装完成</strong><br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210308210343744.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3UwMTQyOTI0MDI=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n在命令行下面输入</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">python</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>看没有python版本提示，出现提示即安装完成。<br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210308210431910.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3UwMTQyOTI0MDI=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n","prev":{"title":"